page_title: 'Quickstart: Use Azure OpenAI Assistants (Preview) via the Azure OpenAI Studio'
page_description: Walkthrough on how to get started with Azure OpenAI and make your first completions call with Azure OpenAI Studio.
chunk_title: Go to the Azure OpenAI Studio
chunk_content: Go to the Azure OpenAI StudioNavigate to Azure OpenAI Studio at https://oai.azure.com/ and sign-in with credentials that have access to your Azure OpenAI resource. During or after the sign-in workflow, select the appropriate directory, Azure subscription, and Azure OpenAI resource.From the Azure OpenAI Studio landing page launch the Assistant's playground from the left-hand navigation Playground > Assistants (Preview):::image type="content" source="../media/quickstarts/assistants-studio.png" alt-text="Screenshot of the Azure OpenAI Studio landing page." lightbox="../media/quickstarts/assistants-studio.png":::
